{"tid":322430,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自己鍾意嘅歌cut左嚟做鈴聲一定唔可以較邊響邊震","createTime":"2017-07-14T20:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T21:59:07.000Z","uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18f974e020453721128705aa36eeaf2a9357a175","tid":322430,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:12:10.000Z","msg":"明明好鍾意首歌<br />\n每次響起加埋震機<br />\n就會有種緊張煩躁嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw雖然打得比我嘅得兩種<br />\n一種係電訊公司提我交電話費<br />\n第二種係美容公司sell鳩me做飛so"},{"pid":"5a39ef79dc936ebcb8ac5ed872da00fb4a76e7e1","tid":322430,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:14:40.000Z","msg":"Btw<br />\n2017年嘅2 月14日曾經有個女仔打過嚟sell me美容套餐<br />\n當時唔捨得cut佢線<br />\n最後是她cut 鳩me的<br />\n很想念她的聲音哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdf949661f5e9a09fd94e080e5b5d35f3ce9783","tid":322430,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:25:06.000Z","msg":"更正：應該係個女仔想約我出嚟<br />\n但me拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3199cd230fd09f329b07dfeb091fce775a0f4e0","tid":322430,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:09:58.000Z","msg":"都冇人打俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae31414a7e61bbbec897c133e63233413b8b8dc","tid":322430,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:59:07.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}